&lt;p class=&quot;p1&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;MLB Voices&amp;nbsp;is a Fellowship Program aimed to develop and grow the next generation of play-by-play talent in &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;baseball, with a specific focus on elevating diverse voices within the game. In 2024, in an effort to broaden the &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;voices delivering baseball to all fans and level the playing field, Major League Baseball, in collaboration with the &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;Black Play-by-Play Grant &amp;amp; Scholarship Fund launched the MLB Voices Program.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;p1&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;Participants selected for this program will gain hands-on opportunities to call play-by-play for select MLB. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;Develops events. Additionally, they will benefit from mentorship and guidance from experienced voices in the &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;baseball broadcasting industry. Over the course of the 10-month program, participants will exit with tangible &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;copies of high-level television broadcast tape, enhancing their professional reels. They’ll also establish valuable &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;connections within MLB, network with peers and MLB clubs at the Baseball Winter Meetings, and attend MLB &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;All-Star Week, with shadowing opportunities and participation in key events like the HBCU Swingman Classic &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;and the Futures Game.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
