&lt;p class=&quot;p1&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;The program is a &lt;strong&gt;10-month&lt;/strong&gt; commitment and runs from &lt;strong&gt;February through November 2026.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
